    "Subsequently, we apply the mapping rule, as detailed below, to derive the final DRG prediction from base DRG and CC/MCC labels.",
    "Process to dissect and derive DRGs to/from base DRGs and CC/ MCC.",
    "We first used regular expression to obtain principal diagnosis/procedures in MS-DRG v.34.0, by extracting strings prior to the description of CC/MCC.",
    "For example, in DRG 11 of \"tacheostomy for face mouth and neck diagnoses with mcc\", the principal diagnosis is \"tacheostomy for face mouth and neck diagnoses\".",
    "After this step, 340 principal diagnosis/procedures are identified as base DRGs."
